'''Hwayi''' (Sheep in English) imhuka inopfuyiwa pamusha iri pamupanda we[[dzinoyamwisa]]. Hwayi dzinopfuyiwa Pasirose; asi nyika dzinoti Australia, New Zealand; neku[[chamhembe]] kwe[[ziwumbe]] reSouth America ndiko kunonyanya kupfuyiwa hwayi.

Hwayi dzinodyiwa nyama uye dzinokamiwa [[mukaka]]. Mamvanda ehwayi anogerwa achigadziriswa fleece neshinda inonzi wool. Pashinda dzinobva pamhuka mamvanda ehwayi aya ndiwo anonyanya kushandiswa Pasirose.

